entries.allies_arrived: We are here my friend. Let's do this!
entries.allies_win: Great job! Setting course for Naboo, see you there!
entries.enemies_arrived: Here they come, get ready everyone!
entries.enemies_remain: Imarrra < Take that you Imperial scum! >
entries.found_loc: Meet up at these coordinates and let's make a break for it there.
entries.quest_findbattle_d: These are the coordinates that you have decided to break through the blockade from. Get there with haste.
entries.quest_helpallies_d: This is it, your Wookiee friends have arrived. Destroy the Imperial attackers fast before more of them arrive!
entries.quest_location_d: The Dathomir system is heavily guarded by the Empire. The only non imperials that dare to venture in here are either really crazy or really skilled. Either way, they are usually a dangerous threat.
entries.title: To the queen's aid, phase III
entries.title_d: You're almost home free. Now you just need to make a hole in the Imperial blockade around the planet for you all to escape. Imarrra and Orrekazzapirr will meet you in their ship above the planet.
